        software products for real estate and property management industry with a special
        focus on Indian Market. Eukleia Technologies is founded by two experienced persons
        in the software industry with a collective experience of over 25+ years across Indian
        service providers and global MNCs. Eukleia Technologies has its registered office
        in Bangalore, India and has a development centre in Hyderabad, India. Details can
        be found on our Contact Us page. NikunjChhaya is a web-based computer-aided facility
        management solution for residential and commercial complexes. Launched in May 2018,
        NikunjChhaya.com has been received extremely well by Apartment Associations and Property
        Developers. Within a very short span of 5 months, the software got good recognitions
        and was among the ten products which were showcased in "Product Launch pad" event
        organized by NASSCOM in November 2018, top 16 SaaS products in NASSCOM SaaS products
        for Indian Market, top 3 product start-ups in the ITsAP Exhibition - a Government
        of Andhra Pradesh annual event. NikunjChhaya is ideally positioned to take advantage
        of the increase in penetration of internet and mobile, continued addition of new
        complexes, and shift towards professionally managed complexes to become a credible
        player in this segment.<br /><br /> 
  
